    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a solid foundation for someone looking for a dependable driver at an accessible price point. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable clear coat failure on the trunk and several small dings along the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat bolster and some staining on the rear carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it will soon require new brake pads and a suspension refresh to restore its original ride quality. It is a reliable workhorse that needs a little cosmetic and mechanical TLC to be brought back to its best.",
